      ],
      "content": "Verify them at the respective PNS developer portal (APNS, GCM, WNS etc) using our <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><ept id=\"p1\">Getting Started Tutorials]</ept>."
    },
    {
      "content": "Azure Management portal",
      "pos": [
        11423,
        11446
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Go to the Configure tab to review and match the credentials with those obtained from the PNS developer portal.",
