    {
      "content": "Visual Studio",
      "pos": [
        11609,
        11622
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "If you use Visual Studio for development then you can connect to Microsoft Azure and view and manage a bunch of Azure services including Notifications Hub from \"Server Explorer\".",
      "pos": [
        11630,
