      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You can view and manage all the registrations in your hub which are nicely categorized for platform, native or template registration, any tags, PNS identifier, registration id and the expiration date.",
      "pos": [
        11883,
        12083
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You can also edit a registration on the fly - which is useful say if you want to edit any tags.",
      "pos": [
        12084,
