      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">[AZURE.NOTE]</ph> Visual Studio functionality to edit registrations should only be used during dev/test with limited number of registrations.",
      "pos": [
        12201,
        12337
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "If there arises a need to fix your registrations in bulk, consider using the Export/Import registration functionality described here - <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><ept id=\"p1\">Export/Import Registrations]</ept> (Only available in Standard Tier)",
